Summary: I was driving East on 35/80 when I saw a disk shaped craft fly North with 2 black helecopters flying after it
divs: sighting detailsi was driving east on 35\80 near mile marker 133.6 when i saw a darker disc fly infront of me (right to left) i then saw 2 black helecopters chasing it. i didnt have any feelings, but my first reaction was to take pictures of what i could. i lost sight of the objects because i was driving on freeway.
